entities.trees

Class TDP_Prefix_Solution

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.trees.TDP_Solution
      • entities.trees.TDP_Prefix_Solution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TDP_Prefix_Solution>

    public class TDP_Prefix_Solution
extends TDP_Solution
implements Comparable<TDP_Prefix_Solution>
    A prefix representation of T-DP solutions that allows for sharing common prefixes. The prefix is with respect to a stage ordering (the same as the stage indexing) that agrees with the tree structure. Each prefix solution consists of one decision and a pointer to a prefix solution of shorter length.
    Author:
    Nikolaos Tziavelis
    See Also:
    TDP_Part
